---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TopBar from '../components/astro/TopBar.astro';
import Header from '../components/astro/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/astro/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Sudsy Co. Washer and Dryer Rental"
  description="Sudsy Co. Rentals privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our washer and dryer rental services."
  canonical="https://www.sudsycorentals.com/privacy-policy/"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <TopBar />
    <Header />
    <div class="hero-gradient py-4">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground">Home</a></li>
          <li>/</li>
          <li class="text-foreground">Privacy Policy</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">
        Last updated: February 25, 2026
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8 text-foreground/90">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            Sudsy Co. Rentals ("we," "our," or "us") operates the website
            <a href="https://www.sudsycorentals.com" class="text-primary underline">sudsycorentals.com</a>
            and provides washer and dryer rental services on the Mississippi Gulf Coast,
            including Gulfport, Biloxi, Ocean Springs, D'Iberville, Long Beach, Gautier,
            Pascagoula, Pass Christian, and Moss Point.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Contact information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and
              mailing address when you submit a contact form, schedule a delivery, or sign
              up for our rental service.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Payment information:</strong> Billing details processed securely
              through our third-party payment processor (Stripe). We do not store your
              credit card numbers on our servers.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Usage data:</strong> Information about how you interact with our
              website, including pages visited, time spent, and referring URLs, collected
              through Google Analytics and Meta Pixel.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Device information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, and IP
              address for security and analytics purposes.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Process and fulfill your washer and dryer rental orders</li>
            <li>Schedule deliveries, installations, and maintenance visits</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your account, orders, and service updates</li>
            <li>Send promotional offers and newsletters (with your consent)</li>
            <li>Improve our website, services, and customer experience</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations and prevent fraud</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p>
            Our website uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your
            browsing experience and analyze site traffic. These include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Google Analytics (G-Q1Y72LG58V):</strong> Helps us understand website
              usage patterns and improve our content.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Google Ads (AW-17921626656):</strong> Used for conversion tracking
              and remarketing to show relevant ads.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Meta Pixel:</strong> Helps us measure the effectiveness of our
              Facebook and Instagram advertising.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings. Disabling
            cookies may affect some website functionality.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">How We Share Your Information</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with trusted
            third parties solely to operate our business:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Payment processors</strong> (Stripe) to handle transactions securely
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Analytics providers</strong> (Google, Meta) to measure site
              performance
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Communication tools</strong> to send order confirmations and service
              notifications
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your
            personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or
            destruction. Payment data is encrypted and processed through PCI-compliant
            services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal information</li>
            <li>Opt out of marketing communications at any time</li>
            <li>Request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for data processing where applicable</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at
            <a href="tel:+12283383455" class="text-primary underline">(228) 338-3455</a>
            or through our website contact form.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our services are not directed to individuals under 18. We do not knowingly
            collect personal information from children.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on
            this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this page
            periodically.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground">Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please
            contact us:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-1">
            <li>
              <strong>Phone:</strong>
              <a href="tel:+12283383455" class="text-primary underline">(228) 338-3455</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Location:</strong> Ocean Springs, Mississippi
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Website:</strong>
              <a href="https://www.sudsycorentals.com" class="text-primary underline">sudsycorentals.com</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
